Obsession and me had a fate together. I literally e-mailed the url to him as a reply to his latest e-mail in December.
He never once returned to the topic. 
I love this song.

I wish to learn from him sometime, since I also kind of dance, but seeing him do all of those things with his body makes me very depressed because reaching that kind of a dance level seems very much impossible for us "mortals". I am truly in awe.
